# Global Rules
- Do NOT say functional, wired, or complete unless verification passes:
  1) tests pass (npm test and/or pytest if present)
  2) scripts/run_optimizer.ps1 runs (or DryRun OK)
  3) scripts/verify_wiring.ps1 passes
  4) artifacts written (machine + human)

- Scripts are the truth: real execution is via scripts/*.ps1; update scripts instead of inventing ad-hoc commands.
- Artifacts contract:
  - artifacts/last_run.json (machine-checkable)
  - artifacts/nba_optimizer_<timestamp>.md (human report)
  - artifacts/logs/*.txt (raw logs)
